text: This section describes the Excel Decoder and Excel Encoder agents which are processing agents for batch workflow configurations. These agents convert Excel files into UDRs to be routed into a workflow, and then converts the UDRs back into an Excel file to be delivered to the output destination. Open Workflow using Excel Encoder and Decoder Agents This section contains the following subsections: Excel Decoder Agent Excel Encoder Agent Excel Agents UDR Types
